~ start_npc_gabbi
do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_activated.emit()
Gabbi: Hi, would you like to help me?
- Yes
	Gabbi: You got a job for me?
	- Yes
		Gabbi: Cool, ill take that
		do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_deactivated.emit() 
	- No
		do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_deactivated.emit() 
		=> END
- No
	Gabbi: Too bad...
do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_deactivated.emit() 
	=> END